The use of matrix multiplication and the mention of the exponents of matrix multiplication suggest that it may also belong to the categories of numerical analysis (cs.NA) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the mention of a stochastic central path method suggests that it may also belong to the category of control systems (cs.SY).
